Rating: 4
This is good but there's another really easy(and tasty!) way to dress up oatmeal. Just cook the oatmeal as you normally would, but substitute milk for the water and add a splash of vanilla. top with brown sugar, butter, and a splash of half and half. As simple as it sounds it's very reminiscent of creme brullee!

